    public interface I_ConstantNumeric
    Centralizes all shared numbered variables since software specifications requires no numbers in the java sources.
    protocols may overload it with their specific constants. Was formerly I_sim_constants
    Author:
    Q.Baduel, 2008, rev. Le Fur 07-09-11.2014, 10.2015
    See Also:
    I_ConstantString
